description:
A full-featured Swiss Army Knife for your brain.

The full-featured mind mapping and brainstorming app. Like a Swiss Army Knife, Xmind offers a complete toolset for thinking and creativity.
Important Updates
1. Introduced a new text style â€” underline;
2. Enabled the import of iThoughts mind map files.
Improvements
1. Grid structure now supports modifying Cell alignment and fill color;
2. Grid structure now supports customizing border styles;
3. Enhanced the auto-naming logic for cloud files;
4. Enabled subscribed Team members to unlock paid features in local files;
5. Fixed an issue where subscribed Team members could not use paid templates;
6. Fixed a potential error when sharing mind maps on the "Recents" page;
7. Fixed an issue where unlogged users were not prompted to log in when saving files to the cloud;
8. Fixed the issue where the search panel did not display incomplete tasks;
9. Fixed the issue where the Note-saving function may fail while pasting;
10. Fixed the issue where copying and pasting Labels in Matrix structure failed;
11. Fixed the issue where topics could not be moved in Outline mode;
12. Fixed the issue where resizing topics or images did not show a bidirectional arrow;
13. Fixed a potential error when repeatedly clicking the "Create Custom Themes" button;
14. Optimized certain UI designs and text;
15. Fixed some other known issues.
